------

If you create the role by using AWS AppConfig, the system also creates the following trust relationship for the role. 

------
#### [ JSON ]

****  

{

  "Version":"2012-10-17",		 	 	 
  "Statement": [
    {
      "Effect": "Allow",
      "Principal": {
        "Service": "appconfig.amazonaws.com"
      },
      "Action": "sts:AssumeRole"
    }
  ]
}

